        "content": "# Creator Support\n\n## Purpose\nThis document defines the specialized support available to creators.\n\n## Creator Support Philosophy\n\n- **Priority**: Creators are priority users\n- **Specialized**: Creator-specific support\n- **Empowering**: Help creators grow\n- **Proactive**: Proactive support\n\n## Creator Support Channels\n\n### Primary Channels\n\n| Channel | Description | Priority |\n|---------|-------------|----------|\n| **Email** | support@blicbloc.com | High |\n| **Help Center** | Creator-specific articles | High |\n| **In-App** | In-app chat (future) | Medium |\n\n### Specialized Support\n\n| Support Type | Description |\n|--------------|-------------|\n| **Onboarding** | Help creators get started |\n| **Technical** | Technical support for publishing |\n| **Growth** | Advice on growing audience |\n| **Monetization** | Help with monetization |\n\n## Creator Support Areas\n\n### Account Support\n\n| Area | Support |\n|------|---------|\n| **MainSpace Creation** | Help setting up MainSpace |\n| **Profile Customization** | Help customizing profile |\n| **Account Issues** | Account and login issues |\n| **Settings** | Account settings |\n\n### Content Support\n\n| Area | Support |\n|------|---------|\n| **Publishing** | Help publishing Blics and Sparks |\n| **Editing** | Help editing content |\n| **Deletion** | Help deleting content |\n| **Troubleshooting** | Content issues |\n\n### Technical Support\n\n| Area | Support |\n|------|---------|\n| **Upload Issues** | File upload problems |\n| **Format Issues** | File format questions |\n| **Performance** | Platform performance |\n| **Bugs** | Bug reporting |\n\n### Growth Support\n\n| Area | Support |\n|------|---------|\n| **Audience** | Growing your audience |\n| **Engagement** | Engaging followers |\n| **Analytics** | Understanding analytics |\n| **Best Practices** | Content best practices |\n\n## Creator Onboarding\n\n### Onboarding Support\n\n| Phase | Support |\n|-------|---------|\n| **Initial Setup** | Help setting up account |\n| **MainSpace** | Help creating MainSpace |\n| **First Content** | Help publishing first content |\n| **Audience** | Help growing audience |\n\n### Onboarding Checklist\n\n| Task | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| **Sign Up** | Complete sign-up |\n| **MainSpace** | Create MainSpace |\n| **First Blic** | Publish first Blic |\n| **First Spark** | Publish first Spark |\n| **Customization** | Customize MainSpace |\n| **Audience** | Share MainSpace |\n\n## Creator Resources\n\n### Help Center Articles\n\n| Topic | Description |\n|-------|-------------|\n| **Getting Started** | Creator getting started |\n| **Publishing** | Creator publishing guide |\n| **Growing** | Growing your audience |\n| **Best Practices** | Creator best practices |\n\n### Educational Content\n\n| Content Type | Description |\n|--------------|-------------|\n| **Blog Posts** | Creator tips and advice |\n| **Guides** | Comprehensive guides |\n| **Webinars** | Live training (future) |\n| **Video Tutorials** | Step-by-step videos |\n\n## Creator Feedback\n\n### Feedback Channels\n\n| Channel | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Support** | Support interactions |\n| **Surveys** | Creator surveys |\n| **Interviews** | Creator interviews |\n| **User Testing** | Feedback sessions |\n\n### Feedback Areas\n\n| Area | Questions |\n|------|-----------|\n| **Platform** | What's working? What's not? |\n| **Features** | What features do you need? |\n| **Support** | How can we improve support? |\n| **Growth** | What would help you grow? |\n\n## Creator Success\n\n### Success Metrics\n\n| Metric | Target |\n|--------|--------|\n| **Creator Retention** | 60%+ after 3 months |\n| **Content Creation** | 4+ Blics per month |\n| **Audience Growth** | 10%+ per month |\n| **Creator Satisfaction** | 90%+ |\n\n### Success Stories\n\n| Content | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Case Studies** | Creator success stories |\n| **Interviews** | Creator interviews |\n| **Testimonials** | Creator testimonials |\n\n## Creator Community\n\n### Community Features\n\n| Feature | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Forums** | Creator forums (future) |\n| **Groups** | Creator groups (future) |\n| **Events** | Creator events (future) |\n| **Networking** | Creator networking (future) |\n\n### Community Support\n\n| Support | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Peer Support** | Creators helping creators |\n| **Mentorship** | Experienced creators mentoring |\n| **Collaboration** | Creator collaboration |\n| **Recognition** | Creator recognition |\n\n## Creator Proactive Support\n\n### Proactive Outreach\n\n| Trigger | Action |\n|---------|--------|\n| **New Creator** | Welcome email, tips |\n| **Inactivity** | Re-engagement email |\n| **Milestones** | Congratulations |\n| **Issues** | Proactive help |\n\n### Proactive Content\n\n| Content | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Tips** | Content tips |\n| **Best Practices** | Best practices |\n| **Updates** | Feature updates |\n| **Resources** | Helpful resources |\n\n## Success Metrics\n\n| Metric | Target |\n|--------|--------|\n| **Creator Satisfaction** | 90%+ |\n| **Creator Retention** | 60%+ |\n| **Response Time** | Under 24 hours |\n| **Resolution Time** | Under 48 hours |\n\n## Next Steps\n\n1. Define creator support channels\n2. Create creator resources\n3. Build creator onboarding\n4. Establish creator feedback\n5. Launch creator support"
